{"tid":2346694,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020回顧] 一人一間/幾間垃圾黃店餐廳","createTime":"2020-12-30T12:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T17:05:53.000Z","uid":37197,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5425da2f689503bad44e6e017bfb40fccd2fc0","tid":2346694,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"喺2020年，好多以黃店打正旗號既餐廳<br />\n無論起食物質素、價錢、服務都唔盡如人意<br />\n我開依個Post係因為好多連登仔對黃店盲目支持<br />\n盲目既支持只會依堆黃店肆無忌憚、無任何誘因去改善佢地既服務質素<br />\n忽略左開餐廳最基本既野--- 質素<br />\n食物，服務質素缺一不可，更甚食物難食，我理你深黃都無用<br />\n一講難食就比人標做五毛，依個風氣完全唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*例如某觀塘台灣店：小時光<br />\n黃店既吃貨之家 貨不對辦重要屌客賣蟹粉小籠包比菜肉包<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2215319/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2215319/page/1</a><br />\n手機維修服務差--發夢手機維修<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2185687/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2185687/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我相信我既食評，好多同路人都會同意，完全無抹黑元素。<br />\n<br />\n1) 厚福街元祖拉麵 - 洗腎之選<br />\n   <br />\n   一入黎送包紙巾比你，好撚貼心喎 ( 屌你埋單原來又收鳩你錢)，綠茶又收錢 ，未聽過日本拉麵店會收你錢 ，聽講依家無再收啦，我果陣食係仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食物： 芝士海膽沾麵，得個鹹字，好稠好杰，碗湯完全無海膽味，成碗野叉燒一舊都無，得幾舊海膽碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麵算正常。<br />\n食完之後要去隔離七仔買一大枝水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單加一 ：大約hkd 120 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (屌你老母咁撚難食 收咁貴)<br />\n<br />\n反應多我再Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668cf55c4fe23f77972456b3458b53458a9565c5","tid":2346694,"uid":39519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"試過見到元祖張枱塊玻璃下面有一條條細細隻嘅白蛆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b17e18e3ce921c337e3d4f4fa143f5aebe7f82","tid":2346694,"uid":73849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"淨係見到元祖已經要推<br />\n難食加濫收費用"},{"pid":"d4dd160452a1e543c1d8d0f1a3a11317079e226a","tid":2346694,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hNcPK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hNcPK4.jpg&h=c3a7caeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Nhz246.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Nhz246.png&h=4b5a2864&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrwUiDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrwUiDr.jpg&h=3603bc0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"487c18c67bb5d05b8399a6f838bb29cc927dfeaf","tid":2346694,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4dd160452a1e543c1d8d0f1a3a11317079e226a","tid":2346694,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hNcPK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hNcPK4.jpg&h=c3a7caeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Nhz246.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Nhz246.png&h=4b5a2864&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrwUiDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrwUiDr.jpg&h=3603bc0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"仲有 甜一刻 cheeky pasta 如意冰室 開餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b6238ca510f051139ffb249b68bc8c0b26af8f","tid":2346694,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"487c18c67bb5d05b8399a6f838bb29cc927dfeaf","tid":2346694,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4dd16